g.text: Backend (express js, zod, dotenv and jest)
High Availability: Kubernetes with 3 control nodes behind a load balancer
Application Load balancer using nginx and upstream servers (HALB optional)
3 control planes to ensure HA if 1 goes down
there are 2 planes to form a majority to take decision
Scale up or scale down as per demand
Container script will run all tests before creating the container
